{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"1":"The Book of Purification"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":324,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":324}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":43,"arabicnumber":43,"text":"اخبرنا اسحاق بن ابراهيم، قال انبانا جرير، عن منصور، عن هلال بن يساف، عن سلمة بن قيس، عن رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم قال \" اذا استجمرت فاوتر","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":43}}]}